official_title: To require the Secretary of the Treasury to mint coins in commemoration of the Vietnam Veterans Memorial on the occasion of the 10th anniversary of the Memorial.
short_title: 1994 Vietnam Veterans Memorial Commemorative Coin Act

summary.text: 1994 Vietnam Veterans Memorial Commemorative Coin Act - Directs the Secretary of the Treasury to issue one-dollar silver coins emblematic of the Vietnam Veterans Memorial. Mandates that surcharges from the sale of such coins be paid to the Vietnam Veterans Memorial Fund to help raise an endowment to be a permanent source of support for the Memorial.
